Class Mutant

  • java.lang.Object
    • Mutant

  • public class Mutant
extends java.lang.Object
    Mutant objects contain the information from the mutant log. The premutation code, the mutated code, status of the mutant, by what method it was killed, by what tests, and the line number.

    jaholtz
